---
title: Sweet Soy Turkey Patties with Roasted Veggies and Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Tender turkey patties are smothered in a sweet soy glaze in this vibrant and balanced plate. Roasted veggies and sweet potato wedges round out the meal without going overboard on calories.

